## Easy
<div class="challenge-body-html"><div class="challenge_problem_statement"><div class="msB challenge_problem_statement_body"><div class="hackdown-content"><svg style="display: none;"><defs id="MathJax_SVG_glyphs"></defs></svg><p>Sometimes it's better to use dynamic size arrays. Java's  <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html">Arraylist</a> can provide you this feature. Try to solve this problem using Arraylist.<br></p>
